CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 7, 1958, pg. A12 reads: "Au Revoir - Pittsburgh Gays said "au revoir" to their guests Sunday at a brunch held at the handsome Aliquippa home of Dr. ad[sic] Mrs. Max Johnson, left. Right, Dr. and Mrs. Carroll Holmes.  She's a Steel City Gay- All Photos by Harris"
TitMainTitle: Woman wearing eyeglasses and hat, and man wearing suit, holding cigar, standing in front of home of Dr. and Mrs. Max Johnson for Gay Northeasterners farewell brunch
